# MU Online S6 Client — Cursor Rules

## 1. CRITICAL CONSTRAINTS (NO EXCEPTIONS)
* **DO NOT BUILD**: AI must NOT run any build/test commands (cmake, ctest, dotnet). User compiles manually.
* **DO NOT PUSH**: AI must NEVER run `git push`. The user handles remote pushes manually (all pushes need to go to https://github.com/andrescolombo/BarnaMuClient).
* **ASK IF UNSURE**: If the AI has any ambiguity, doubts, or is not 100% sure about requirements or design decisions, it **MUST** stop and ask clarifying questions instead of guessing.

